{
  "stem": "18778.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Cuban immigration permits, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have copies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have these-- some of these letters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found them only recently, maybe a couple of years ago, among my mother's papers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother only passed away about two and a half years ago, and so I didn't know all the material that she still had, besides what I already had.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these people said we'd pay-- everybody seemed to have paid a different price for these papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my-- I have correspondence that I went over last night where my father addressed the Cuban authorities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was absolutely no way that anybody was willing to give any kind of money back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow or other, people were able to scrape together-- perhaps through Jewish organizations, perhaps through private contributions-- the monies to pay for the passage to the United States.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure where our passage money came from.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, we, we left London the end of August.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our ship was leaving from Glasgow, Scotland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While my father was interned, the blitz of London had begun, and I had returned to London to be with my mother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had raids every day and, specifically, every night for the next three months-- June, July, August.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother and I ended up in the air-raid shelter every single night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Each-- we lived, at that time, in a rooming house in Willesden Green, which is in the northwest [INAUDIBLE] area of London, a nice neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The house belonged to a couple of teachers who made it a rooming house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't live there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And each room held a family of refugees, not necessarily-- there were two St.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Louis families in this house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a Polish opera singer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were Belgian refugees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was quite a mixture.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
